collections.name: Faith Attention Time
collections.description:
Thoughts...
were my main enemy.

They were killing me,
taking the last air inside.

They were breaking the connection with the world and with people.

They were creating chaos, anxiety and fear,
covering my eye with a black cloud.

I could not even imagine
that this would become a lesson of fate:
Faith - Attention - Time,
the solution to all my problems.

... we stopped believing.

... attention only to anger.
to the trash surrounding us,
to the unnecessary moments of everyday life.

... and time has long been under control - by the past and the future.

Time is no longer valued,
not believing and not noticing it.

The main thing is not just to listen - but to hear,
not just to understand - but to realize:

... faith will help you neither to die,
nor to lose yourself and not to give up in the end.

Attention will allow you to understand everything,
to realize everything and move on.

Time will forgive and let go,
put everything in its place,
and with time you will find yourself.

collections.name: Fear Pain Shame
collections.description:
It's scary to live with the thought that I can't love anymore.

It hurts that it's not meant to be with the one for whom my soul cries.

It's a shame that it was my fault, and I realized it only now.

Fear - Pain - Shame,
The consequence of Love from the other side.

You'll hardly read and immediately understand,
Just not with her, it won't work.

Where she is, thoughts are not important,
Where she is, the heart boils, feelings tear the soul from the inside.

The mind asks for it all to stop,
After all, it knows that the feelings of Love are neither in it nor in the body.

Only the soul decides how to live,
Only the soul knows how to be.

Only the soul does not know who it is.

Constantly runs, hiding in the shadows,
Afraid to open up to others.

The wound is festering, doesn't know how to heal,
Because it's afraid,
Afraid to open up.

#Fear_Pain_Shame

TO, which became the beginning of the creation of fate,
Proving the existence of true will.

With gambling eyes erasing the line between reality,
With an immoral state reflecting the flesh of the dark devil.
The author of which is whoever he is, the creator of duakhalnosti himself.

collections.description:
Home is Family.
What is more important than all material goods.

And we don't care where we will be tomorrow,
Or where we are now.
We will always be at home,
Drinking tea together...

In which the roof and foundation,
This is free will and the value of life,
Where our soul and body live.

#Home_Family

collections.name: Fallen Angel
collections.description:
Fallen angel falling,
Crashed on the karma of the soul,
Turning into a number of bright rays.

He did not ask for forgiveness and did not expect redemption,
He did not think about the place and malice towards himself.

He decided to give up life and death,
For the sake of saving stupid people.

As a creation of God without a soul,
Noble actions,
He became like this?

The first thing he did,
Gave people Light.
In their eyes, in their hearts,
In their bodies and souls.

Secondly,
He saw what is not visible from heaven.
A lost dead soul,
Above the bodies of many people.

He helped them finish,
Their unfinished path,
Freeing our mental burden. 

#Fallen_Angel

collections.name: Moves my World
collections.description:
The cyclical nature of events speaks of one thing,
There is something that must come true.
Any choice is made by me,
Eventually leads to what I need.

Welcome to my amazing world.
Everything is unique in it,
A look, a feeling, a worldview.

Every day is unusual in its own way,
Every year in its own way,
Every moment surprises more and more.

A year has passed, we met,
And you say that I am completely different.
That is why it is so difficult for me to answer who I am.
After all, I am constantly finding a new part of myself.

#Moves_my_World
